high_descs: Walk straight towards the tub and face the right end of it
Pick up a tissue from the tub top
Turn to the left and face the middle of the tub
Place the tissue in the bottom of the tub
Turn to the right and face the right end of the tub
Pick up a tissue from the tub top
Turn to the left and face the middle of the tub
Place the tissue in the bottom of the tub
anns.task_desc: Collecting tissues to put in the bath tub

high_descs: Walk forward to the rags next to the bathtub.
Pick up the rag closest to the bathtub.
Turn left and walk to the bathtub.
Place the rag in the bathtub.
Turn around and walk to the rags next to the bathtub.
Pick up the rag farthest away from you.
Turn left and walk to the bathtub.
Place the rag next to the other rag in the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Place two rags inside the bathtub.

high_descs: Walk forward to tub.
Pick up tissue closest to tub rim.
Turn left walk to middle of tub then right.
Drop tissue in tub.
Turn right walk to wall then left at counter.
Pick up tissue closest to rear wall.
Turn left walk to middle of tub then right.
Drop tissue in tub.
anns.task_desc: Pick up tissues, drop them in the tub.

high_descs: Walk forward towards the bath tub
Pick up a rag off of the counter
Move a few steps to your left
Drop the rag into the bath tub
Walk back to the counter on your right
Pick up another rag off of the counter
Return back to the bath tub on your left
Drop the second rag into the bath tub
anns.task_desc: Drop two rags into a bath tub
